text:
Good job, Chiyoko.
That was a great live performance...!

If it was a great experience for Chiyoko too,
then I'm really happy.
It seems like all the preparation paid off!

Haha... Of course,
I shouldn't be completely satisfied yet, but...

─But, being on stage with everyone from
the agency and all the amazing idols.

wearing matching outfits,
and giving our best together...
─It made the live performance so much fun!
So, I think today was a big success!
